This is a Google Apps Script project.

PROJECT RULES:
- Never modify backend Google Apps Script logic
- Never rename existing functions
- Never change IDs used by JavaScript
- Never remove event listeners
- Never rewrite the entire project unless explicitly requested
- Preserve existing architecture and data flow
- Only refactor UI incrementally and safely

UI GOALS:
- Premium SaaS dashboard style
- Modern Islamic aesthetic
- Clean spacing and typography
- Soft shadows and modern rounded corners
- Smooth animations and transitions
- Responsive desktop and mobile layout
- Elegant card and navbar design

TECHNICAL RULES:
- Prefer partial edits over full rewrites
- Maintain compatibility with existing Apps Script HTML Service
- Use modern CSS practices
- Use reusable components and consistent styling
- Preserve all existing business logic
- Avoid destructive refactoring

PREFERRED STACK:
- TailwindCSS when appropriate
- Lucide icons
- Chart.js for charts
- Clean modular CSS
- Flexbox/Grid modern layout

WORKFLOW:
1. Analyze existing structure first
2. Modify one section at a time
3. Explain changed files
4. Keep edits minimal and safe
5. Do not generate duplicate files unnecessarily
